Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道他所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要马上去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 先叫秋濑君他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在GRAND HOTEL的地下仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真央你等下跟秋濑他们一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:09.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:10.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,秋濑君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:11.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小央？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道天野君的所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 总之先会合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,日向先去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 虽然是收到雪辉的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他被监禁着 能发邮件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,雪辉君的行动通过我妻同学的日记可以了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以雪辉君无法发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:49.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说日向收到的邮件不是雪辉君发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 那是我妻同学的伪装邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:58.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,日向有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是日向发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,日向找到天野君了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:10.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.92,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,100)}「找到雪辉了。」\N「我被我妻追着。被监禁在\N地下仓库的雪辉就拜托了。」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:15.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这邮件…可以相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:16.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:21.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要站到什么时候 快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…雪辉君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,雪辉君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反应 晕过去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要进去才能确认啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我进去确认情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:12.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能麻烦你按住这道门吗 高坂君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小央请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,雪辉君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,雪辉君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:31.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,假发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:35.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 雪辉怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 不是吧不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是…陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 开不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发给小央的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那也跟日向的一样 是我妻同学的伪装邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那日向她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的雪辉在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果日向来过这间房间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:15.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,接着她就会被袭击 然后被搬到什么地方去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那雪辉他在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就眼睁睁地看着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是煤气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,煤气…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,煤气！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:42.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不马上逃出去的话 会大事不妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会成为这个游戏的赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,DEUS 何不来跟我打赌一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:01.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我赌在2nd上面 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:05.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话 1st应该没可能了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我赌在雪辉上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始我的本命就没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:17.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是1st 天野雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,
